FREE DELIVERY!

Built to your specification by our experts

We build every gaming PC to order - starting with your choice of components and assembled by a fully-trained technician.

If choosing one of our core series PCs, these usually take between 1 and 3 working days to complete from receipt of the order.

If choosing one of our 'Turbo Charged' SG series, your PC is a little more complicated than our standard line-up and can take on average 3-5 working days to complete from receipt of the order.

Once the PC has been built, QC'd and tested by the team, the PC will be dispatched which across the UK should take a maximum of 2 working days (but is often 1 in most areas).

Free Delivery*

At OGEN, we build every Gaming PC to order. This means our customers have full customisation over every aspect of their systems. See our Custom PC Builder. Of course, that means there are a few stages your OGEN Gaming PC needs to go through before we clear it for dispatch. We promise it will be worth the wait.

Dispatch

Its been picked. Its been built. Its been checked and its been tested. Its time to get it out to you. We use bespoke packaging for every gaming computer, specially designed to fit the case youve chosen. We then double down on the packaging (better to be safe than sorry!) and add any discs, cables, freebies and accessories you may have on your order. From then on, we put your new Vibox PC in the careful hands of our couriers, (DPD in the UK, DPD or FedEx across Europe), and send you a tracking number to the email address youve provided us with.

Delivery

On the morning of delivery, youll receive an email and a text from the courier with an estimated delivery time. If youre in the UK, you can take advantage of DPDs Predict Service, which allows you to follow your drivers progress on your PC or smartphone, with live-updates so you know exactly when to expect your new PC.

Our Warranty

In 2015, we put a few new Gaming PCs out for review. While we were thrilled with the feedback regarding the spec, performance and build quality, there were some less positive comments about our warranty. We have full confidence in the quality of our PCs, so we decided to put our money where our mouth is, and created the Vibox Evolution Gold Warranty. This warranty package, which comes as standard with every OGEN PC, is the only standard warranty in the UK to offer a lifetime of upgrades, repairs and support free of charge. You can find all the details and T&Cs at the foot of the page, but heres a summary of what you can expect with every OGEN PC:

LIFETIME REPAIR & UPGRADE LABOUR

As long as you have your OGEN PC, youll never have to pay any labour charges for repairs or upgrades. Should any components develop a fault (it can happen!), well never charge you to install replacements. If you fancy adding a little more power to your gaming computer, well fit any new parts free of charge, making your new Vibox the last PC youll ever need to purchase

LIFETIME TECHNICAL SUPPORT

Every now and then, its natural youll need a little bit of help with your PC. If youre looking to get a little more out of your system or your games, well talk you through the best options. If youre looking to upgrade, well make sure youre getting the best deal for your money. If youre having a technical issue or a part has a fault, well do our best to pin down the exact nature of the issue and get it resolved as quickly as possible. The best way to contact us is by using our chat widget or following the details on our Support page, or by giving us a call on 0161 425 8841

2 YEARS PARTS COVER

While we do run tests on every component before shipping our Gaming PCs out. Sadly the nature of computers means that parts can fail. Thats why we offer a full 2 years parts cover on every component in your Gaming PC. We dont repair components here, so in the case of a fault well simply provide a brand new replacement and install it free of charge.

180 DAYS COLLECTION + RETURN

Were so confident in the quality of our gaming computers that should anything go wrong in the first six months, well send a courier to collect your PC at our expense. After that, well be able to book a collection on your behalf with DPD, at a discounted rate. Were proud to offer the best standard warranty in the business, but if youre looking for something even better, we also offer the Evolution Platinum Warranty. It has all the benefits of the Gold warranty but with 3 Years of Parts, Collection and Return cover service, which allows you to follow your drivers progress on your PC or smartphone with live-updates so you know exactly when to expect your new machine.

UK Support

At OGEN, we build every Gaming PC to order. Please dont hesitate to let us know if you need any help with a sales query, if you need some help with your new Vibox PC, or if for any reason youre not satisfied. Were here to help and will do everything we can to resolve any issues or queries you may have. If you need to get in touch with for any reason, there are a couple of ways to do so:

Email

You can reach us at ogen.co.uk@gmail.com. If you have an issue could you please include your name, address, order number and detail the problem you are experiencing and well get back to you as soon as possible. Our email support is available in English, French, German, Spanish and Italian, and we aim to respond to all queries within 24 hours, Monday-Friday.

Phone

Alternatively, if youd like to give us a call, you can do so on 0161 425 8841. Calls from the UK will be charged at your standard local rate. If youre calling from abroad it may cost more, and it may be best to email us and request a call-back. Our UK-based phone support team will be able to offer assistance in English, French and Spanish.

At OGEN, we provide top-quality Custom Gaming PCs! Each one of our gaming computers is designed by gamers, for gamers and is built by fully trained, experienced technicians. Our custom and Pre-built Gaming PCs come with lifetime support and upgrade labour as part of our Evolution Warranty, so it may well be the last PC you'll ever need to buy!
